#. Content instruction
msgid "If the respondent was living outside the UK on Sunday {census_date}, please explain that they do not need to complete the rest of the questionnaire and end interview. <p>You still need to submit this questionnaire.</p><p> Continue past the household members summary page and select Submit.</p>"
msgstr "Os oedd yr ymatebwr yn byw y tu allan i’r Deyrnas Unedig ddydd Sul {census_date}, esboniwch nad oes rhaid iddo lenwi gweddill yr holiadur a dewch â’r cyfweliad i ben.<p>Bydd dal angen i chi gyflwyno'r holiadur hwn.</p><p> Ewch ymlaen heibio'r crynodeb o aelodau'r cartref a dewiswch Cyflwyno.</p>"

#. Content instruction
msgid "If the respondent was not living at the property on census night, but other current household members were, you must speak to one of those household members instead. <p>If none of those household members are available, <strong>save and sign out</strong> of the questionnaire. You must return to the address to interview one of them at a later time or date.</p>"
msgstr "Os nad oedd yr ymatebwr yn byw yn y cartref ar noson y cyfrifiad, ond bod aelodau presennol eraill o’r cartref yn byw yno, rhaid i chi siarad ag un o’r aelodau hynny o’r cartref yn hytrach na’r ymatebwr. <p>Os nad oes dim un o’r aelodau hynny o’r cartref ar gael, <strong>cadwch yr holiadur ac allgofnodwch</strong>. Rhaid i chi ddychwelyd i’r cyfeiriad er mwyn cyfweld ag un ohonynt rywbryd eto.</p>"

#. Content instruction
msgid "Only complete this section once all other sections are answered"
msgstr "Dim ond ar ôl cwblhau'r holl adrannau eraill y dylech gwblhau'r adran hon"

#. Content page description
msgctxt "Your household"
msgid "All the questions are about the people in your household on Sunday {census_date}."
msgstr "Mae pob un o’r cwestiynau’n ymwneud â’r bobl a oedd yn eich cartref chi ddydd Sul {census_date}."

#. Content page description
msgctxt "Your household"
msgid "A <strong>household</strong> is one person living alone, or a group of people (not necessarily related), who share cooking facilities <em>and</em> share a\n"
"        living room, <strong>or</strong> sitting room, <strong>or</strong> dining area."
msgstr "Mae <strong>cartref</strong> yn golygu un person sy’n byw ar ei ben ei hun, neu grŵp o bobl (nid oes rhaid iddyn nhw berthyn i’w gilydd), sy’n rhannu cyfleusterau coginio <em>ac</em> yn rhannu ystafell fyw <strong>neu</strong> lolfa <strong>neu</strong> le bwyta."

#. Content page description
msgctxt "Your household"
msgid "Some of the questions that I will ask have showcards to help you to answer."
msgstr "Bydd gan rai o’r cwestiynau y byddaf yn eu gofyn gardiau dangos er mwyn eich helpu chi i ateb."

#. Content page description
msgctxt "Your household"
msgid "I will show you these on paper or on the phone screen."
msgstr "Byddaf yn dangos y rhain i chi ar bapur neu ar sgrin y ffôn."

#. Content page description
msgctxt "<em>Interviewer Note</em>"
msgid "If none of the household members were usually living at the property on census night, you must save and sign out of the survey and complete a paper questionnaire."
msgstr ""

#. Content page description
msgctxt "Household and accommodation"
msgid "In this section, I’m going to ask you about the household and accommodation you were living in on Sunday {census_date}"
msgstr "Yn yr adran hon, byddaf yn gofyn i chi am y cartref roeddech chi’n byw ynddo ddydd Sul {census_date}"

#. Content page description
msgctxt "{person_name}"
msgid "In this section, I’m going to ask you questions about <em>{person_name}</em>"
msgstr "Yn yr adran hon, byddaf yn gofyn cwestiynau i chi am <em>{person_name}</em>"

#. Content page description
msgctxt "{person_name}"
msgid "In this section, I’m going to ask you about your visitor, <em>{person_name}</em>"
msgstr "Yn yr adran hon, byddaf yn gofyn i chi am eich ymwelydd, <em>{person_name}</em>"

#. Content page description
msgctxt "Final check – other households"
msgid "These final questions are to check we have not missed any other living accommodation or households"
msgstr "Diben y cwestiynau olaf hyn yw gwneud yn siŵr nad ydym ni wedi colli unrhyw gartref neu fan arall lle mae rhywun yn byw"

#. Question text
msgid "Were you usually living at {household_address} on Sunday {census_date}?"
msgstr "Oeddech chi’n byw yn {household_address} fel arfer ddydd Sul {census_date}?"

#. Question text
msgid "What is your full name?"
msgstr "Beth yw eich enw llawn?"

#. Question text
msgid "Was anyone in your current household usually living here on Sunday {census_date}?"
msgstr "Oedd unrhyw aelod o'ch cartref presennol fel arfer yn byw yma ddydd Sul {census_date}?"

#. Question text
msgid "On Sunday {census_date}, was your usual address in the UK?"
msgstr "Ddydd Sul {census_date}, oedd eich cyfeiriad arferol yn y Deyrnas Unedig?"

#. Question text
msgid "What was your household’s usual address?"
msgstr "Beth oedd cyfeiriad arferol eich cartref?"

#. Question text
msgid "I will now collect the names of everyone who lived at that address on Sunday {census_date}"
msgstr "Byddaf nawr yn casglu enwau pawb a oedd yn byw yn y cyfeiriad hwnnw ddydd Sul {census_date}"

#. Question text
msgid "Who do you need to add?"
msgstr "Pwy y mae angen i chi ei ychwanegu?"

#. Question text
msgid "Change details for <em>{person_name}</em> (You)"
msgstr "Newid manylion <em>{person_name}</em> (Chi)"

#. Question text
msgid "Change details for <em>{person_name}</em>"
msgstr "Newid manylion <em>{person_name}</em>"

#. Question text
msgid "Did anyone else usually live in your household on Sunday {census_date}?"
msgstr "Oedd unrhyw un arall fel arfer yn byw yn eich cyfeiriad ddydd Sul {census_date}?"

#. Question text
msgid "Are you sure you want to remove <em>{person_name}</em>?"
msgstr "Ydych chi'n siŵr eich bod am ddileu <em>{person_name}</em>?"

#. Question text
msgid "Apart from the people already included, is there anyone else who was temporarily away or staying that you need to add?"
msgstr "Ar wahân i’r bobl sydd wedi’u cynnwys eisoes, oes unrhyw un arall oedd i ffwrdd o’r cartref dros dro neu’n aros dros dro y mae angen i chi ei ychwanegu?"

#. Question text
msgid "Are any of these people related to each other?"
msgstr "Oes unrhyw rai o'r bobl hyn yn perthyn i'w gilydd?"

#. Question text
msgid "How many visitors were staying overnight at {household_address} on Sunday {census_date}?"
msgstr "Faint o ymwelwyr oedd yn aros dros nos yn {household_address} ddydd Sul {census_date}?"

#. Question text
msgid "How many visitors were staying overnight at {other_address} on Sunday {census_date}?"
