#. Question text
msgid "Are all the rooms in this accommodation, including the kitchen, bathroom and toilet, behind a door that only this household can use?"
msgstr "Ydy pob ystafell yn y cartref hwn, gan gynnwys y gegin, yr ystafell ymolchi a’r toiled, y tu ôl i ddrws sydd ddim ond yn cael ei ddefnyddio gan aelodau o’r cartref hwn?"

#. Question text
msgid "Were all the rooms in that accommodation, including the kitchen, bathroom and toilet, behind a door that only this household could use?"
